name: Worth & Soul
description:
Wrecks Of Men
Nothing Against Your Conscience
Sons Of Horus
Great Minds & Fools
Blood & Soil
Blame The Martyr
Seeds
Worth & Soul

Recorded at Claycastle Studios and Blue Box Studios 2011

Release on Sep 10th 2011

"Brain twistingly brutal vocals and dirty down tuned churning riffs paint a bleak and sordid sonic picture. But FWD don't just leave it there. They amalgamate it all with a nice ambient touch that rounds off the whole affair with great effect."

http://ridewiththedevil.blogspot.com
